This module is used to stop/start the modem


WHAT IT DOES?
=============
md_ctrl is used to stop/start the modem

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library from AOSP:

libc liblogwrap liblog libcutils

HOW TO USE IT?
==============
Run md_ctrl as a daemon/service. For example, create a service in init*.rc on
an Android platform.

The majority of source code were written by MediaTek.
